---
import Button from "../../shared/Button.astro";
---

<div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-top">
        <div class="hero-top-left">
            <h3>Soluciones Digitales para el Crecimiento de tu Negocio</h3>
        </div>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10" height="80%" viewBox="0 0 4 175" fill="none">
            <path d="M2 2L1.99999 173" stroke="#8493B6" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="hero-top-right">
            <p>
                Creamos conceptos visualmente impactante y altamente creativo, que destaquen la identidad de tu marca. Estrategicamente destamos los contendidos, para que tengan algo mas que contar, que les genere valor a todos los niveles de la corporaci√≥n
            </p>
            <div class="hero-top-right-bottom">
                <div class="hero-top-right-bottom-item">
                    <div class="hero-top-right-bottom-item-top">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
                            <ellipse cx="9.98055" cy="10" rx="9.90291" ry="10" fill="#D9D9D9"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h1>+75.000</h1>
                    </div>
                    <p>Lectores De Nuestro Clientes</p>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-top-right-bottom-item">
                    <div class="hero-top-right-bottom-item-top">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
                            <ellipse cx="9.98055" cy="10" rx="9.90291" ry="10" fill="#D9D9D9"/>
                        </svg>
                        <h1>+ 100.000</h1>
                    </div>
                    <p> Impresiones Realizadas</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-bottom">
        <div class="hero-bottom-img">

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .hero
    {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 30px;
        justify-content: space-between;
        height: 100%;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero-top
    {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        text-align: center;
        gap: 100px;
    }

    .hero-top-left
    {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    .hero-top-left h3
    {
        width: 90%;
        text-align: left;
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero-top-right p
    {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 200;
        color: #818181;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .hero-top-right
    {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 25px;
    }

    .hero-top-right-bottom
    {
        display: flex;
        gap: 20px;
        justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    .hero-top-right-bottom-item-top
    {
        display: flex;
        gap: 15px;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-bottom
    {
        flex-basis: 70%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .hero-bottom-img
    {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        position: relative;
        border-radius: 30px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 20px;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        color: #FFF;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-bottom-img::before
    {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background-image: url("https://i.imgur.com/yfIBb7m.jpeg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        opacity: 1;
        z-index: -1;
        border-radius: 30px;
        padding: 100px;
    }

    .hero-bottom-title
    {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
    }

    .hero-bottom-title h3
    {
        font-size: 40px;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero-bottom-title p
    {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 200;
        color: #818181;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 767px)
    {
        .hero
        {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        h1
        {
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 40px;
        }

        p
        {
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1024px)
    {
        .hero
        {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 30px 65px;
        }

        h1
        {
            width: 50%;
            font-size: 40px;
        }

        p
        {
            width: 50%;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    }
</style>